item.description:
This is the 3rd week of a karaoke contest. (You can compete as many weeks as you want.) There haven't been enough contestants to fill a whole evening [7-10 contestants], so the evening will start (at 8 PM) with non-contest karaoke requests. Most contestants haven't been arriving until 9 PM or later and the dj hasn't been starting the contest until around 10:15. This could change if a much larger number of contestants show up.
There is no cover charge and no fee to compete.
item.how_to_find_us: I'll either wear my NEIL cap or have a name tag.
